description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Zoodle Salad recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken Zoodle Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spread a little dressing onto plates. Top with rocket, zucchini, avocado, prosciutto, olives and chicken. Season with pepper. Serve.
